title: Songs That Remind Us Of Our Childhood + Bobby Feud: Best Candy Bars In America + Taylor Acorn Blows Us Away With Her Performance!
itunes:title: Songs That Remind Us Of Our Childhood + Bobby Feud: Best Candy Bars In America + Taylor Acorn Blows Us Away With Her Performance!
description:
Bobby, Amy and Eddie songs that share a special place in their hearts because it reminds them of their childhood. We play the Bobby Feud and try to name the Top 10 Chocolate Bars in America. New Artist Taylor Acorn stops by and performs her song “Like the Movies”.
